          <span class="testimonial-author">— Newsweek</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">"Disney+ Lost Nearly 3 Million Subscribers After Jimmy Kimmel Suspension"</p>
          <span class="testimonial-author">— Fox Business</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">"Spike in Disney+ cancellations after Kimmel suspension"</p>
          <span class="testimonial-author">— BBC</span>
        </div>
        <!-- Duplicate for seamless loop -->
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">"Disney reportedly lost 1.7 million subscribers during Kimmel's suspension"</p>
          <span class="testimonial-author">— The Street</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">"Disney adults know how to hit where it hurts"</p>
          <span class="testimonial-author">— Salon</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">"Jimmy Kimmel's reinstatement shows the power of noncooperation"</p>
          <span class="testimonial-author">— Waging NonViolence</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">"Disney Plus Subscribers Quit in Droves Over Jimmy Kimmel Axe"</p>
          <span class="testimonial-author">— Newsweek</span>
        </div>
